DocWhereRule.Name: WR31
DocWhereRule.Documentation: The inherited name for pre defined items shall only have the value of one of the following words.
DocWhereRule.Expression: SELF\IfcPreDefinedItem.Name IN ['blanked arrow','blanked box', 'blanked dot','dimension origin','filled arrow','filled box', 'filled dot','integral symbol','open arrow','slash','unfilled arrow']
